    "raw": "The First Contact war made the Skath into one of the most paranoid races in the known galaxy. While they will deny that it is fear, and instead chalk it up to 'nerves', there is no doubt to the classic fight-or-flight response a Skath enters when startled. So imagine just how paranoid they could get with *planning* behind it.",
